data.description: NEW HVAC, NEW ROOF AND SOLAR all within the last 3yrs. Average monthly electric bill is $30mo!! Discover tranquility in this charming manufactured home ON FOUNDATION, nestled among the trees in a serene neighborhood just minutes away from downtown Emmett. This gem enjoys a peaceful location with a large two-car carport and convenient storage shed accessible via the alley. Automatic sprinklers AND SIDEWALKS adorn the fenced yard and water is provided by irrigation. Cozy up by the pellet stove, and rest easy knowing that both the stove and chimney have been recently cleaned. Water Softener  and kitchen appliances included. Bedrooms are LARGE! Experience the best of Emmett – a blend of quiet living and proximity. Don't miss the chance to call this delightful home your. NO HOA! Do what you want hassle free.
